text: Patriarch Jacob may refer to: * Patriarch Jacob of Alexandria * Patriarch Jacob I, Maronite Patriarch of Antioch in 1141–1151 * Patriarch Jacob II, Maronite Patriarch of Antioch in 1277–1278 * Patriarch Jacob III, Maronite Patriarch of Antioch in 1445–1468 * Patriarch Jacob IV, Maronite Patriarch of Antioch in 1705–1733
title: Patriarch Jacob
